#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Between 2021 and 2023 Tails, [Tor](https://torproject.org/), and the "
"[Guardian Project](https://guardianproject.info/) partnered to organize "
"training and usability tests in Ecuador, Mexico, and Brazil. Our goals were "
"to:"
msgstr ""
"Zwischen 2021 und 2023 haben sich Tails, [Tor](https://torproject.org/) und "
"das [Guardian Project](https://guardianproject.info/) zusammengetan, um "
"Schulungen und Nutzertests in Ecuador, Mexiko und Brasilien zu organisieren. "
"Unsere Ziele waren:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Promote our digital security tools and train human rights defenders in the "
"Global South."
msgstr ""
"Förderung unserer digitalen Sicherheitsinstrumente und Schulung von "
"Menschenrechtsverteidigern im globalen Süden."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Learn from their experiences and needs to help us prioritize future work."
msgstr ""
"- Aus ihren Erfahrungen und Bedürfnissen lernen, um uns bei der "
"Priorisierung zukünftiger Arbeiten zu unterstützen."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Improve the usability of our tools based on their feedback."
msgstr ""
"- Verbessert die Benutzerfreundlichkeit unserer Werkzeuge basierend auf "
"ihrem Feedback."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Usability tests and improvements"
msgstr "Benutzerfreundlichkeitstests und -verbesserungen"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We conducted 4 rounds of in-person moderated usability tests in Mexico, "
"Brazil, and Ecuador to identify usability issues in the features of Tails "
"that are most important to new users:"
msgstr ""
"Wir haben 4 Runden moderierter Usability-Tests vor Ort in Mexiko, Brasilien "
"und Ecuador durchgeführt, um Usability-Probleme in den Funktionen von Tails "
"zu identifizieren, die für neue Benutzer am wichtigsten sind:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Installation"
msgstr "- Installation"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Tor Connection"
msgstr "- Tor Verbindung"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Persistent Storage"
msgstr "- Beständiger Datenspeicher"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The DesignOps tools that we used to organize these usability tests are all "
"[[publicly available on our website|contribute/how/user_experience]]."
msgstr ""
"Die DesignOps-Tools, die wir verwendet haben, um diese Usability-Tests zu "
"organisieren, sind alle [[öffentlich auf unserer Website verfügbar|"
"contribute/how/user_experience]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The detailed methodology for each of the usability tests is explained in the "
"corresponding GitLab issues, linked below."
msgstr ""
"Die detaillierte Methodik für jeden der Usability-Tests wird in den "
"entsprechenden GitLab-Issues erklärt, die unten verlinkt sind."

#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Installation"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In December 2021 in Mexico, we learned that the tools for new users to "
"install Tails worked well, but several people got lost while navigating the "
"instructions on the website."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Based on these findings, we restructured our installation pages and fixed 30 "
"usability issues on the website."
msgstr ""
"Basierend auf diesen Ergebnissen haben wir unsere Installationsseiten "
"umstrukturiert und 30 Usability-Probleme auf der Website behoben."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We tested these improvements in August 2022 in Brazil and confirmed that the "
"new installation pages were much easier to follow. Only 1 out of 4 "
"participants had trouble installing Tails on their own. All participants "
"could start Tails and connect to the Tor network easily."
msgstr ""
"Wir haben diese Verbesserungen im August 2022 in Brasilien getestet und "
"festgestellt, dass die neuen Installationsseiten viel einfacher zu verstehen "
"sind. Nur 1 von 4 Teilnehmern hatte Probleme, Tails selbst zu installieren. "
"Alle Teilnehmer konnten Tails starten und sich problemlos mit dem Tor-"
"Netzwerk verbinden."

