#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Assistants to the workshops were able to start Tails on all their PC "
"computers but had more frequent issues with Mac computers."
msgstr ""
"Die Assistenten der Workshops konnten Tails auf allen ihren PC-Computern "
"starten, hatten jedoch häufigere Probleme mit Mac-Computern."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"From what is already possible to do with Tails, people were most interested "
"in using Tails to:"
msgstr ""
"Von dem, was bereits mit Tails möglich ist, waren die Menschen am meisten "
"daran interessiert, Tails zu verwenden, um:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Handle sensitive data, for example, medical data of abortion patients, "
"sensitive documents from political trials, or field studies from human "
"rights violations. That said, not all journalists thought that they were "
"manipulating data that was sensitive enough to require a tool like Tails.  "
"Sometimes it was hard to draw the line on when to use Tails and when not."
msgstr ""
"Gehen Sie mit sensiblen Daten um, zum Beispiel mit medizinischen Daten von "
"Abtreibungspatienten, sensiblen Dokumenten aus politischen Prozessen oder "
"Feldstudien zu Menschenrechtsverletzungen. Dennoch dachten nicht alle "
"Journalisten, dass sie mit Daten arbeiteten, die sensibel genug waren, um "
"ein Werkzeug wie Tails zu benötigen. Manchmal war es schwierig, die Grenze "
"zu ziehen, wann Tails verwendet werden sollte und wann nicht."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Investigate sensitive topics online, either for journalistic purposes, "
"medical purposes, or when making safe travel plans."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Have a secure OS when using other people's computer, either when traveling "
"or when people don't have the means to have their own computer."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"From what is not possible yet to do with Tails, people were most interested "
"in:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Doing online meetings and using mobile messaging apps like Signal and "
"Telegram from Tails."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Using a VPN instead of Tor for speed and access to more websites."
msgstr ""
"- Verwendung eines VPNs anstelle von Tor für mehr Geschwindigkeit und "
"Zugriff auf weitere Webseiten."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We included both of these objectives in our 3-year product strategy.  You "
"can track our progress in the GitLab issues related to [[!tails_ticket "
"19472]]."
msgstr ""
"Wir haben beide Ziele in unsere 3-Jahres-Produktstrategie aufgenommen. Sie "
"können unseren Fortschritt in den GitLab-Issues zu [[!tails_ticket 19472]] "
"verfolgen."
